PYTHON¶

After my master’s degree, due to my passion for programming lenguages, I decided to study independently Python and some of its modules:

  • numpy
  • Pandas
  • Matplotlib/plotly
  • Sql3lite
  • Urllib
  • Tkinter
  • Tensor Flow

I also followed a brief online course on MySQL.

This has allowed me to improve in dealing with large amount of data and their visualization.

GIS¶

Throughout the Telerilevamento exam i had the opportunity to experience for the first time QGIS and remote sencing and, therefore, the various satellites, their orbit, spatial resolution, spectral resolution, temporal resolution, ecc. I've also learned the basic equations to convert a raster file in an information (ex. NDVI). I also have used Arcgis for a brief period during my internship.

I have also improved my QGIS knowledge with raster and vectors and I've acquired a lot of useful plugins.
